<h2 id="the-role">The Role</h2>

<p>We need a Systems Administrator who can handle diverse IT infrastructure for healthcare practices. This is hands-on technical work supporting critical business operations where downtime directly impacts patient care.</p>

<h3 id="primary-responsibilities">Primary Responsibilities:</h3>

<ul>
