  <li>Enterprise Active Directory - multi-site management, trust relationships, security policies</li>
  <li>Virtualization platforms - Proxmox and VMware administration and maintenance</li>
  <li>Linux server administration - system maintenance, security updates, troubleshooting</li>
  <li>Storage systems - RAID configuration, monitoring, and failure recovery</li>
  <li>Level 1-2.5 technical support - escalated helpdesk issues and infrastructure problems</li>
  <li>Client communication - professional, clear explanations of technical issues and solutions</li>
</ul>

